Class SmartLabel

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SmartStylableNode, javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class SmartLabel
extends javafx.scene.text.Text
implements SmartStylableNode
    A label contains text and can be attached to any SmartLabelledNode.
    This class extends from Text and is allowed any corresponding css formatting.

      • setStyleClass

        public void setStyleClass(java.lang.String cssClass)
        Description copied from interface: SmartStylableNode
        Applies the CSS styling defined in class selector cssClass. The cssClass string must not contain a preceding dot, e.g., "myClass" instead of ".myClass". The CSS Class must be defined in smartpgraph.css file.
        Specified by:
        setStyleClass in interface SmartStylableNode
        Parameters:
        cssClass - name of the CSS class.
